thread.title: BRIEF-Guangzhou Boji Medical & Biotechnological to swing to loss in FY 2017

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Guangzhou Boji Medical & Biotechnological to swing to loss in FY 2017

organizations.name: reuters) - guangzhou boji medical & biotechnological co ltd

text:
Feb 1 (Reuters) - Guangzhou Boji Medical & Biotechnological Co Ltd :
* Sees to swing to net loss at 24 million yuan to 29 million yuan in FY 2017 versus net profit at 2.1 million yuan year ago
* Says increase in periodic cost and costs of clinical research service business as main reasons for the forecast
